run out of content. Moreover, while Facebook loses some top-line revenue =
=E2=80=94 in an auction-based system, less demand corresponds to lower pric=
es =E2=80=94 the companies that are the most likely to take advantage of th=
ose lower prices are those that would not exist without Facebook, like the =
